{
  "stem": "12029.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you couldn't do nothing about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And also there were Polish women, which knew rich people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they used to, when they wanted a nice fur coat or something, then they called the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The Germans went in and took out from the Jewish houses fur coats, clothes, whatever those Polish women wanted.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They used to come, and they used to collect.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But that was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was Hanukkah 1939, '40.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the Germans gave an order that every Jew has to wear an armband with a-- it was a white armband, about 10 centimeters wide with a star of David.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then say could recognize every Jew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did you feel about that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very bad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when you went out, people looked at you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They knew straight away that you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they also form-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not a committee, a Jewish, like we've got here, the [? boat ?] of [? guardian. ?] It was a Jewish [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] place, where they used to look after the Jews, which were in Poland.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the chairman of that committee, the president, was a Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Chernyakow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And in 19-- for new year, the Germans gave an order-- they were building a wall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody knew what it is all about.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then they said they are going to make a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they built the wall around Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they said everybody has to come and to live in that part of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Funny enough--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- our flat was in that--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, compound.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father's family lived in Praga.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
